                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">SQL Server 2000 Fast Answers for DBAs and Developers:  <BR>- An easy-to-use, day-to-day desk reference.  <BR>- For all junior, part-time, and reluctant SQL Server DBAs and developers. <BR>- Fast facts to help you get the job done SQL Server 2000 is the leading relational database for the Windows platform.  <BR>- Useful for both beginners and more experienced SQL Server professionals.  <P>This book enables you quickly to reference the specifics of a command or process, bringing you up-to-date with the technology, and helping you refine your craft. SQL Server 2000 Fast Answers for DBAs and Developers gives you:  <BR>- Thorough 'How to' answers to typical SQL Server database administration and developement questions  <BR>- A task-based guide to key parts of the job  <BR>- Installation, configuration, backup, security, replication, failover clustering, DTS, performance, and job automation  <BR>- Conceptual overviews that show how all the parts fit together  <BR>- Useful and concise syntax examples  <BR> - A place to look when you don't know the answer</span>
              
